---
import GitHubIcon from "../icons/GitHubIcon.astro";
---

<div
  class="flex flex-col bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-xl p-6 hover:bg-slate-700/80 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-all group"
>
  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Portfolio Web</h3>
  <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4 flex-1 text-sm leading-relaxed">
    Portfolio Web realizado para dar a conocer mis habilidades adquiridas en mi
    educación superior y proyectos los cuales realicé a lo largo de mi
    formación. <br />
    Proyecto Personal de desarrollo de este portfolio web desarrollado con:
  </p>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
    <img
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/astro/astro-original.svg"
      alt="Astro"
      title="Astro"
      class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 bg-white/90 rounded-sm p-1"
    />
    <img
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/tailwindcss/tailwindcss-original.svg"
      alt="Tailwind CSS"
      title="Tailwind CSS"
      class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
    />
    <img
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/javascript/javascript-original.svg"
      alt="JavaScript"
      title="JavaScript"
      class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 rounded-sm"
    />
  </div>

  <a
    href="https://github.com/yovngmamba8/Portfolio_Ariel_Valverde"
    target="_blank"
    rel="noopener noreferrer"
    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 font-medium transition-colors mt-auto"
  >
    <GitHubIcon class="w-5 h-5" />
    Ver codigo en GitHub
  </a>
</div>
